H3.text: By what name is comic book villain Oswald Chesterfield Cobblepot better known. Cobblepot

A4.text: The Penguin (so called because his stature resembles that of a penguin) (Oswald Chesterfield Cobblepot) is a fictional character

A5.text: The Penguin is one of Batman's most enduring enemies and belongs to the collective of adversaries that make up Batman's rogues gallery
